high_descs: Turn right. Go straight ahead. Enter through the first entrance on the left. Go to the dresser. Cross to the right and then to the left. Turn to face the dresser.
Take the apple.
Turn around, move until you are next to the plate. Turn left in front of the plate.
Place the apple on the plate.
Take the plate and the apple.
Leave the room. Turn left. Reach the end of the corridor. Turn left. Go inside and stand in front of the diningtable.
Place the plate and the apple on the left side of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Find an apple and a plate. Bring them to the diningtable.

high_descs: Turn right to head down the passage and turn left to walk down the passage and reach the dresser.
Pick up the apple from the dresser.
Turn right to face the plate.
Put the apple on the plate on the bed.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Turn around to walk down the passage to the end and turn left to reach the diningtable.
Put the plate on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the apple on the plate on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the dresser.
Take the apple from the dresser.
Turn around and go near the plate.
Put the apple on the plate.
Take the plate with apple from the bed.
Turn around and go near the dining table.
Put the plate on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Placed the plate with apple on the dining table.
